OL,4,Ccould cost 'extra #3bn'
OL,6,FPay rises for teachers and NHS staff
OL,7,Fcould cost an extra #3 billion if the
OL,8,Fgovernment implements a 5.5% increase
OL,9,Fto wages, according to the Institute
OL,10,Fof Fiscal Studies (IFS).
OL,12,FIt has been reported that independent
OL,13,Fpay review bodies will recommend the
OL,14,F5.5% rise, which is likely higher than
OL,15,Fministers were expecting.
OL,17,FPaul Johnson, director of the IFS,
OL,18,Fsaid he was "not terribly surprised"
OL,19,Fby the figure, which would be in line
OL,20,Fwith pay rises across the economy.
