OL,3,CPay rises for teachers and NHS staff
OL,4,Ccould cost 'extra #3bn'
OL,6,FHe said: "In terms of the cost, there
OL,7,Fisn't a specific number that is
OL,8,Fbudgeted for schools, it's probably 1
OL,9,For 2%, it's certainly nothing like
OL,10,F5.5%, so we'd certainly be looking at
OL,11,Fat least an additional #1 billion on
OL,12,Fschools' costs relative to what
OL,13,Fthey're currently expecting.
OL,15,F"And a number at least double that
OL,16,Facross the NHS if the proposals for
OL,17,Fthe NHS are similar, which it appears
OL,18,Fthat they might be."
