OL,4,Ccould cost 'extra #3bn'
OL,6,FMr Johnson added that if the 5.5%
OL,7,Ffigure was replicated across the
OL,8,Fpublic sector, it could mean the
OL,9,Fgovernment needs to find an extra #10
OL,10,Fbillion.
OL,12,FA higher-than-expected pay rise could
OL,13,Fpose a significant challenge for
OL,14,FRachel Reeves's first budget, likely
OL,15,Fto come in the autumn, after promising
OL,16,Fto control borrowing and ruling out a
OL,17,Fstring of tax rises during the
OL,18,Felection campaign.
