OL,3,CPay rises for teachers and NHS staff
OL,4,Ccould cost 'extra #3bn'
OL,6,FSchools and hospitals are unlikely to
OL,7,Fbe able to meet a 5.5% pay rise from
OL,8,Ftheir existing budgets without making
OL,9,Fcuts elsewhere.
OL,11,FAsked where the money could come from,
OL,12,FMr Johnson said: "The answer is the
OL,13,Fsame as the answer always is when
OL,14,Fasked: where can the money come from?
OL,16,F"It can only come from higher
OL,17,Fborrowing than they're planning,
OL,18,Fhigher taxes than they're planning or
OL,19,Fcuts in spending elsewhere.
OL,21,F"There is no fourth option here."
