OL,3,CPay rises for teachers and NHS staff
OL,4,Ccould cost 'extra #3bn'
OL,6,FBut failing to meet the
OL,7,Frecommendations of the pay review
OL,8,Fbodies, expected to be published this
OL,9,Fmonth, would set up a clash with trade
OL,10,Funions representing the six million
OL,11,Fpublic sector workers.
OL,13,FDaniel Kebede, general secretary of
OL,14,Fthe National Education Union, warned
OL,15,Fthat ignoring the recommendations of
OL,16,Fpay-review bodies could result in
OL,17,Fstrike action.
