OL,4,Ccould cost 'extra #3bn'
OL,6,FNoting that the new Education
OL,7,FSecretary, Bridget Phillipson, had
OL,8,F"worked really hard" to improve
OL,9,Frelations with the teaching
OL,10,Fprofession, he said: "It would be
OL,11,Fhighly problematic for the Treasury to
OL,12,Fthen intervene and then not implement
OL,13,Fa 5.5% pay award.
OL,15,F"We absolutely would want to avoid
OL,16,Fstrike action, but that would almost
OL,17,Fseem inevitable if the Treasury were
OL,18,Fto make such an intervention."
